{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"81bda44ff7","title":"代拟的给陈宗娥的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f50a95911","index":0,"year":1962,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"81bda44ff7"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"7f85f338e8","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这封信是以江青名义写给曾在毛泽东家做过保姆的陈宗娥的。徐业夫，当时任毛泽东办公室秘书。"},{"id":"f226cccd98","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"云鹤，即李云鹤，江青的原名。"}],"contents":[{"id":"34e09f664e","type":"title","text":"代拟的给陈宗娥的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"},{"id":"7f85f338e8","type":"paragraph","text":"宗娥：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"},{"id":"f226cccd98","type":"paragraph","text":"你1961年6月27日给我的信，我于今天早上才收到。在北京压了十个半月，真是当有此理！至于你说，去年三月有信，则至今未收到，正在查询。我已两年不在北京了，患了重病，不习北方气候。现病略为好些，忽（勿）以为念。闻你如此重病，又如此困难，心极不安。今送上五百元，以济眉急。如有所需，望随时告我。有病不要性急，越急越坏。安心治疗，是为上策。有信请写：北京中南海17支局109号信箱徐业天同志收转江青。祝你健康！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"},{"id":"6a395b2491","type":"subtitle","text":"云鹤","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"},{"id":"dda3b11088","type":"paragraph","text":"1962年5月12日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"},{"id":"9c0050c5b8","type":"paragraph","text":"H这封信是以江青名义写给曾在毛泽东家做过保姆的陈宗娥的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7"}],"page":{"id":"01a28decad","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"81bda44ff7","start":140,"end":140}}}},"__N_SSG":true}